makeNameBeUserid

void makeNameBeUserid()
Make the name of this user be the same as the userid. This is done when (a) this user's name isn't in fact the userid (due to nickname change tracking) and (b) a new user logs in with the name that this user currently has.

getIRCUserid

java.lang.String getIRCUserid()
Get the IRC userid for this user. This may be different from getName() if the userid did a name change while we were watching.

Returns:
the IRC userid
